### 2. HQML → MyBatis Mapper 동적 쿼리 변환표

| HTOMSS (HQML) | tomms-lite (MyBatis) |
|---------------|----------------------|
| `<isNotEmpty property="field">` | `<if test="field != null and field != ''">` |
| `<isEmpty property="field">` | `<if test="field == null or field == ''">` |
| `<isEqual property="field" compareValue="value">` | `<if test="field == 'value'">` |
| `<isNotEqual property="field" compareValue="value">` | `<if test="field != 'value'">` |
| `<isGreaterThan property="field" compareValue="10">` | `<if test="field > 10">` |
| `<isLessThan property="field" compareValue="10">` | `<if test="field < 10">` |
| `#field#` | `#{field}` |
| `$field$` | `${field}` |

### 3. Oracle → MariaDB SQL 함수 변환표 ⭐

**중요**: HTOMSS는 Oracle 기반이지만, **tomms-lite는 MariaDB 기반**입니다!

| 기능 | Oracle (HTOMSS) | MariaDB (tomms-lite) |
|------|----------------|---------------------|
| **날짜 포맷** | `TO_CHAR(date, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')` | `DATE_FORMAT(date, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%s')` |
| **문자열 결합** | `'A' \|\| 'B'` | `CONCAT('A', 'B')` |
| **LIKE 검색** | `LIKE '%' \|\| #{text} \|\| '%'` | `LIKE CONCAT('%', #{text}, '%')` |
| **현재 날짜** | `SYSDATE` | `NOW()` |
| **NULL 처리** | `NVL(field, default)` | `IFNULL(field, default)` |
| **조건식** | `DECODE(field, 'A', 1, 2)` | `CASE WHEN field='A' THEN 1 ELSE 2 END` |
| **페이징** | `ROWNUM`, `ROW_NUMBER()` | `LIMIT #{size} OFFSET #{offset}` |
| **듀얼 테이블** | `SELECT 1 FROM DUAL` | `SELECT 1` |

**페이징 변환 예시**:

```xml
<!-- Oracle (HTOMSS) -->
<select id="selectList">
    SELECT * FROM (
        SELECT ROWNUM AS RNUM, A.* FROM (
            SELECT * FROM TB_INVENTORY
            ORDER BY CREATE_DATE DESC
        ) A
        WHERE ROWNUM <= #{pageNo} * #{pageSize}
    )
    WHERE RNUM > (#{pageNo} - 1) * #{pageSize}
</select>

<!-- MariaDB (tomms-lite) -->
<select id="selectList">
    SELECT * FROM TB_INVENTORY
    ORDER BY CREATE_DATE DESC
    LIMIT #{pageSize} OFFSET #{offset}
    <!-- offset = (pageNo - 1) * pageSize -->
</select>
```

### 3. Service 메서드 패턴

**조회 (SELECT)**:
```java
@Override
@ServiceId("{화면코드}/selectList")
public List<ResDto> selectList(ReqDto request) {
    logger.debug("Service Method : selectList, Input Param={}", request.toString());
    
    // Validation
    if (!StringUtils.hasText(request.getField())) {
        throw new IllegalArgumentException("필드는 필수입니다.");
    }
    
    try {
        // DAO 호출
        List<ResDto> result = dao.selectList(request);
        
        logger.debug("목록 조회 완료: {} 건", result.size());
        return result;
        
    } catch (Exception e) {
